data:
Using ReasonML/Ocaml to extend the language with novel new features, such as
examples for inexhaustive pattern matching when inconsistencies are present.

Leading lab sections, holding office hours, and actively seeking to improve
existing course material (e.g. I redid our lab slides on DP with 100+ new
slides.)

Here I collaborate with other developers to create interesting real world
projects, such as a Fintech app, and an app for keeping track of your
friend group's incredible Lore.

I worked with MDining to identify areas where we could reduce palm oil
consumption. To do this, I developed a Python script to estimate palm oil
from thousands of product's ingredient list.
